{"tid":1918743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ITZY 新專輯大展自信魅力　〈WANNABE〉奪四榜冠軍！","createTime":"2020-03-10T09:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T13:19:54.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a46fe12ba6bd3d8a09aa965e01d838f6fea703c9","tid":1918743,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"大家應該都聽過 ITZY 昨晚推出的最新專輯了吧？挾著更進化的氣勢，她們果然也征服了音源榜！<br />\n<br />\n以今天（10 日）上午的數據為準，ITZY 昨天傍晚發行的迷你二輯〈IT&rsquo;z ME〉主打歌 &ldquo;WANNABE&rdquo;，在 NAVER Music、Genie、Bugs 和 Soribada 四個音源網站的即時榜上都拿下了冠軍；MV 的人氣也直線上升，不到一天 1000 萬觀看次數已近在眼前。<br />\n<br />\n因應防疫措施，昨晚 ITZY 透過全球直播舉行回歸 showcase，不僅表演了最新主打歌，也帶來風格截然不同的收錄曲 &ldquo;24HRS&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n「我們都很努力，想為各位粉絲打造出讓他們覺得自豪的專輯。」ITZY 昨天在 showcase 上透露：「這次想讓大家看見最有 ITZY 色彩的風格，還有 ITZY 五人在一起時最完美的面貌。我們會持續帶著好音樂、好表演來和大家見面的！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/124952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F124952&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=331609fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/124952</a>"},{"pid":"0eca20771ca2c92eddc5945283732b0608b67986","tid":1918743,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/7bc3fd73a5c257df2b8dfbe5e5104b99/23e4cbfcb4a8a5e5-02/s400x600/67f508150c1a1dbbbf34cb615efaa8a797af8b50.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F7bc3fd73a5c257df2b8dfbe5e5104b99%2F23e4cbfcb4a8a5e5-02%2Fs400x600%2F67f508150c1a1dbbbf34cb615efaa8a797af8b50.gifv&h=319d73fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/0c9560b915326eba6fb2463901e9ad79/23e4cbfcb4a8a5e5-15/s400x600/ced088c0a628678f13a9c01d72dcbd37c834df5b.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F0c9560b915326eba6fb2463901e9ad79%2F23e4cbfcb4a8a5e5-15%2Fs400x600